## Slider Field

A numeric field rendered as a draggable slider, with configurable min, max, and step.

### Usage

```ts
import { CardDef, field, contains } from 'https://cardstack.com/base/card-api';
import SliderField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/slider';

export class Example extends CardDef {
  @field volume = contains(SliderField, {
    configuration: { min: 0, max: 100, step: 1 },
  });
}
```

See the **Examples** section of this spec for the full set of supported configuration options.
